body: 2 more years later @jazzboy, still top notch
This shit takes me back to when I was a little fool.

It's really something, I've read this back in another website but seeing this again is a refresh, alongside with some humor here and there, overall, good art, good story, good fap, my three things I like to see (well and do too) （≧∇≦）
Till this day this still holds up as one of the best ever drawn. I might be exaggerating because it's the first I ever read but still amazing no less.
